ATA Chapter: 32 – Landing Gear
S1000D DMC: 32-41-01-04-00A-720A-P


This task is critical for:

    - Preventing brake overheat and fade due to excessive lining wear

    - Maintaining compliance with minimum wear limits specified by the Brake Manufacturer CMM

    - Enabling in-service brake life tracking, part serial traceability, and return-to-service compliance

    - Ensuring wear pin accuracy without wheel/tire or heat shield removal


